# a BotKit example that interacts with [Cisco DevNet events](https://developer.cisco.com/site/devnet/events-contests/events/)

A bot example to discover BotKit conversations & context storage features,
started from [DevNet Events](https://github.com/CiscoDevNet/node-sparkbot-samples/tree/master/examples/devnet) Cisco Spark bot.


![](img/devnetbot-help-next.png)



![](img/devnetbot-about-conversation.png)


# How to run

[Create a custom bot](https://api.slack.com/bot-users) and paste your bot token below.

```
> git clone https://github.com/ObjectIsAdvantag/devnet-botkit-sample
> cd devnet-botkit-sample
> npm install
....
# Paste your token here
> token=YOUR_BOT_YOKEN node bot.js
...
```
